Configuration and Environment Management

---
description: Configuration and Environment Management
globs:
  - "config/**/*.py"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Place all parameter-loading logic in config/config.py.
- Load .env once, at startup.
- Never modify .env.bak
- Validate critical environment variables; fail fast if they are missing.
